The paper deals with the problem of private information retrieval, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The concept of robustness is related to fault tolerance, which is a topic in distributed systems (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The capacity analysis involves mathematical techniques such as series expansion and optimization, which are also relevant to computational complexity (cs.CC).
